translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_8cf9c040:

    # Z "Anyway, what brings you here?"
    Z "De todos modos, ¿qué te trae por aquí?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:412
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_6b7c5f4f:

    # Ka "{i}*chuckles*{/i} I not mind, [persistent.player_name]. I know I was not expected."
    Ka "{i}*risilla*{/i} No me importa, [persistent.player_name]. Sé que no me esperabas."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:415
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_7d4e8fe9:

    # Z "Make yourself at home. Are you feeling hungry?"
    Z "Siéntete como en casa. ¿Tienes hambre?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:416
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_9e44c416:

    # Z "If you heard Emilia, dinner should be ready soon."
    Z "Si has oído a Emilia, pronto estará lista la cena."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:419
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_424d7b9e:

    # Ka "Is okay if I greet [W], yes?"
    Ka "¿Está bien si saludo a [W], sí?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:420
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_c9291d68:

    # Ka "Maybe I can help with dinner a bit..."
    Ka "Quizá pueda ayudar un poco con la cena..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:423
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_c83be3da:

    # Z "Sure, she will be happy to see you."
    Z "Claro, se alegrará de verte."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:426
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_7f923161:

    # "Kateryna heads towards the kitchen..."
    "Kateryna se dirige a la cocina..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:429
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_64fd50e8:

    # Zt "She seems like a sweet girl."
    Zt "Parece una chica dulce."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:430
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_f22d2cc1:

    # Zt "Igor didn't tell me she was any good in the kitchen."
    Zt "Igor no me dijo que fuera buena en la cocina."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:431
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_b0a972c0:

    # Zt "Maybe I should go take a look at how things are going in there. The wait is making me a little peckish..."
    Zt "Quizá debería ir a echar un vistazo a cómo van las cosas allí. La espera me está dando un poco de hambre..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:435
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_3152b651:

    # "You enter the kitchen..."
    "Entras en la cocina..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:442
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_077b469a:

    # "The knives hitting a chopping board is the only sound that greets you as you walk in on the preparations of your meal..."
    "Los cuchillos golpeando una tabla de cortar es el único sonido que te saluda mientras entras en los preparativos de tu comida..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:445
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_c2c9cc07:

    # W "..."
    W "..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:448
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_7349b53d:

    # Ka "In my country, we boil many things, but I have learned of spices, from uncle Igor. He says is important to put spice early, let oil soak in flavor at start of cooking."
    Ka "En mi país, hervimos muchas cosas, pero he aprendido de las especias, gracias al tío Igor. Dice que es importante poner las especias pronto, dejar que el aceite se impregne de sabor al principio de la cocción."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:449
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_3a0d6f9a:

    # Ka "After that, we add meat to sear it. Vegetables separate. This is how you do here too, yes?"
    Ka "Después, añadimos la carne para dorarla. Las verduras se separan. Así es como se hace aquí también, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:452
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_ec3c28e8:

    # W "It's not much different, yes."
    W "No es muy diferente, sí."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:455
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_47e4d778:

    # Ka "Is not, it takes longer. Now I add bread to thicken broth and add... body, is right word?"
    Ka "Si no, tarda más. Ahora añado pan para espesar el caldo y añado... cuerpo, ¿es la palabra correcta?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:458
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_c2c9cc07_1:

    # W "..."
    W "..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:461
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_85371941:

    # W "I see your hunger is getting the best of you..."
    W "Veo que el hambre te supera..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:466
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_d73524cf:

    # Z "You're not wrong."
    Z "No te equivocas."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:467
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_1e4082e4:

    # Z "Kateryna was interested in contributing. I got curious about how that would go."
    Z "A Kateryna le interesaba contribuir. Tenía curiosidad por saber cómo iría eso."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:470
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_a650fb76:

    # "You hug her from behind..."
    "La abrazas por detrás..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:471
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_da7cbbcc:

    # Z "What are you preparing today, hm?"
    Z "¿Qué estás preparando hoy, um?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:472
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_85c6ce4e:

    # W "I started making stew, nothing too special. But then she came in here, and is giving it a different twist..."
    W "Empecé a hacer un guiso, nada muy especial. Pero entonces entró ella, y le está dando un toque diferente..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:475
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_84005fb0:

    # "Kateryna ignores the two of you, completely focused on the pots and pans in front of her."
    "Kateryna os ignora a los dos, completamente concentrada en las ollas y sartenes que tiene delante."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:476
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_8df28122:

    # W "At first she suggested to mix up the recipe a little. I have let her take the initiative and now look at her, basically doing her own thing."
    W "Al principio sugirió mezclar un poco la receta. Le he dejado tomar la iniciativa y ahora mírala, haciendo básicamente lo suyo."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:477
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_35ce3692:

    # W "She really seems to know what she's doing though. You will have to let me know what you think of it. "
    W "Sin embargo, parece que sabe muy bien lo que hace. Tendrás que hacerme saber lo que piensas de ella."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:481
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_51af1716:

    # Z "I wanted to see you two working together."
    Z "Quería veros trabajar juntas."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:482
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_21b700a6:

    # Z "Kateryna's visit was not planned after all, and she should be sitting with us, rather than serving us in our own house..."
    Z "La visita de Kateryna no estaba planeada, después de todo, y debería estar sentada con nosotros, en lugar de servirnos en nuestra propia casa..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:483
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_25815252:

    # Z "But she sounded like she really wanted to help, so..."
    Z "Pero parecía que realmente quería ayudar, así que..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:486
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_a650fb76_1:

    # "You hug her from behind..."
    "La abrazas por detrás..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:487
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_2b0155f6:

    # Z "What do you think?"
    Z "¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:488
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_131bb23b:

    # W "I think it's nice that she visited us today."
    W "Me parece bien que nos haya visitado hoy."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:491
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_84005fb0_1:

    # "Kateryna ignores the two of you, completely focused on the pots and pans in front of her."
    "Kateryna os ignora a los dos, completamente concentrada en las ollas y sartenes que tiene delante."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:492
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_9685656e:

    # W "After a first shy greeting, she asked if she could lend me a hand."
    W "Tras un primer saludo tímido, me ha preguntado si podía echarme una mano."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:493
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_5709dc45:

    # W "And now look at her, she has taken over the whole kitchen. I am impressed. Or maybe this is her trying to impress us."
    W "Y ahora mírala, se ha hecho cargo de toda la cocina. Estoy impresionada. O tal vez sea ella la que intenta impresionarnos a nosotros."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:497
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_addfb0e3:

    # Z "It's taking longer than usual, so I came to see if everything was alright."
    Z "Está tardando más de lo normal, así que he venido a ver si todo iba bien."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:500
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_a650fb76_2:

    # "You hug her from behind..."
    "La abrazas por detrás..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:501
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_312a5418:

    # Z "So, how is she doing? What do you think?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿cómo le va? ¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:502
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_025813ec:

    # W "I can't complain, really."
    W "No puedo quejarme, la verdad."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:505
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_84005fb0_2:

    # "Kateryna ignores the two of you, completely focused on the pots and pans in front of her."
    "Kateryna os ignora a los dos, completamente concentrada en las ollas y sartenes que tiene delante."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:506
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_39090369:

    # W "It may take a little longer, husband. But I think you will be happy with the tradeoff."
    W "Puede que tarde un poco más, marido. Pero creo que estarás contento con la compensación."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:507
translate spanish kitchen_kateryna_intro_cb864a0e:

    # W "She surely knows what she's doing in the kitchen, and it might be interesting to see if I can learn some foreign dishes from her."
    W "Seguro que sabe lo que hace en la cocina, y podría ser interesante ver si puedo aprender de ella algunos platos extranjeros."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:514
translate spanish kk26_4e4ad678:

    # Ww "Be honest, [persistent.player_name]..."
    Ww "Sé sincero, [persistent.player_name]..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:515
translate spanish kk26_17c5a820:

    # Ww "That's not the only reason you came here, right?"
    Ww "Esa no es la única razón por la que has venido aquí, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:516
translate spanish kk26_c355c200:

    # Ww "Surely you are interested in her not just for her cooking...?"
    Ww "Seguro que te interesa no sólo por su cocina..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:522
translate spanish kk26_44df91aa:

    # Z "She intrigues me, you know this."
    Z "Ella me intriga, lo sabes."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:523
translate spanish kk26_c9a2727d:

    # Ww "See, I know my husband."
    Ww "Ves, conozco a mi marido."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:527
translate spanish kk26_e8e3e0ee:

    # Z "No. I really am just very hungry, today."
    Z "No. En realidad, hoy tengo mucha hambre."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:528
translate spanish kk26_ba96330d:

    # Ww "Hmm, I see."
    Ww "Ya veo."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:530
translate spanish kk26_3ec2d412:

    # W "If you ask me, I wouldn't mind another helping hand in the kitchen."
    W "Si me preguntas a mí, no me importaría tener otra ayuda en la cocina."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:532
translate spanish kk26_0ab21afc:

    # W "Emilia is a good maid, but her cooking skills aren't very reliable. I've had to toss out the occasional dish..."
    W "Emilia es una buena criada, pero sus habilidades culinarias no son muy fiables. He tenido que desechar algún que otro plato..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:535
translate spanish kk26_9dc38dc9:

    # "You step towards Kateryna..."
    "Das un paso hacia Kateryna..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:538
translate spanish kk26_d90f2230:

    # Z "How's it going here?"
    Z "¿Cómo va todo por aquí?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:539
translate spanish kk26_1efb9b68:

    # Ka "Just fine, I think."
    Ka "Bien, creo."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:542
translate spanish kk26_66385583:

    # Ka "I ask to help with meal a little."
    Ka "Pido ayudar un poco con la comida."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:543
translate spanish kk26_5b1b1b9e:

    # Ka "I add some spices, let potatoes cook longer before adding meat. Where I come from, we add more water to process. Not so dry."
    Ka "Agrego algunas especias, dejo que las patatas se cocinen más tiempo antes de añadir la carne. De donde vengo, añadimos más agua al proceso. No está tan seco."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:546
translate spanish kk26_72634007:

    # Ka "It looks better now. You will taste difference!"
    Ka "Ahora se ve mejor. ¡Notarás la diferencia!"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:550
translate spanish kk26_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:551
translate spanish kk26_edab570a:

    # Z "It does look great, indeed. Very good."
    Z "Tiene muy buen aspecto, en efecto. Muy bueno."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:554
translate spanish kk26_c7a0cf0f:

    # Z "Maybe I should have a taste-"
    Z "Quizá debería probarlo..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:557
translate spanish kk26_f498cf52:

    # Ka "No!"
    Ka "¡No!"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:558
translate spanish kk26_7c051698:

    # Z "...?!"
    Z "¡¿...?!"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:561
translate spanish kk26_4ae067ee:

    # Ka "Sorry, [persistent.player_name], is not ready yet."
    Ka "Lo siento, [persistent.player_name], aún no está listo."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:562
translate spanish kk26_9a54c278:

    # Ka "You must wait."
    Ka "Debes esperar."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:565
translate spanish kk26_c314e8e3:

    # Z "{i}*chuckles*{/i} If you say so."
    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} Si tú lo dices."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:566
translate spanish kk26_1ffaffb5:

    # Zt "I haven't seen her so assertive before. She seems to be in her element here."
    Zt "No la había visto antes tan firme. Aquí parece estar en su elemento."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:569
translate spanish kk26_2e03f36e:

    # Z "I will leave you two to it."
    Z "Os dejaré a vosotras dos con ello."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:572
translate spanish kk26_68ca476c:

    # "You head back to the dining room and wait."
    "Te diriges de nuevo al comedor y esperas."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:573
translate spanish kk26_3fd78cf8:

    # "Eventually, [W] comes out, a bowl in her hand..."
    "Finalmente, [W] sale, con un cuenco en la mano..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:576
translate spanish kk26_db17a4f3:

    # W "It's ready. Do you want to see what she prepared?"
    W "Está listo. ¿Quieres ver lo que ella ha preparado?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:579
translate spanish kk26_2a762c14:

    # W "I've had a taste, but I will let you be the judge of it."
    W "He probado un poco, pero dejaré que seas tú quien lo juzgue."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:582
translate spanish kk26_8831f094:

    # W "[persistent.player_name], while you're eating, I have a request..."
    W "[persistent.player_name], mientras comes, tengo una petición..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:585
translate spanish kk26_84a45203:

    # Z "What's on your mind?"
    Z "¿Qué tienes en mente?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:588
translate spanish kk26_8cffaf0e:

    # W "I was thinking to have a private talk with our guest."
    W "Estaba pensando en tener una charla privada con nuestra invitada."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:589
translate spanish kk26_f7c45247:

    # W "I want to learn more about her, and find out exactly why she decided to visit us today."
    W "Quiero saber más sobre ella, y averiguar exactamente por qué ha decidido visitarnos hoy."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:592
translate spanish kk26_aca99a81:

    # W "Don't worry, I won't do anything bad to her."
    W "No te preocupes, no la haré nada malo."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:593
translate spanish kk26_413c3031:

    # W "{i}*giggles*{/i}"
    W "{i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:595
translate spanish kk26_89b921c1:

    # W "Just like with Emilia, I am curious about what she is looking for exactly."
    W "Al igual que con Emilia, tengo curiosidad por saber qué busca exactamente."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:597
translate spanish kk26_11e5bb56:

    # W "But as you know, I like to know the girls who visit your house."
    W "Pero, como sabes, me gusta conocer a las chicas que visitan tu casa."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:600
translate spanish kk26_022ec039:

    # W "Would you mind if I keep her entertained whilst you eat?"
    W "¿Te importa que la entretenga mientras comes?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:603
translate spanish kk26_ccc12d7d:

    # Z "Why would I? Go. Get to know her better."
    Z "¿Por qué iba a hacerlo? Ve. Conócela mejor."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:606
translate spanish kk26_6c02ad1c:

    # W "Alright then. Love you, [persistent.player_name]."
    W "Muy bien, entonces. Te quiero, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:607
translate spanish kk26_43d26487:

    # W "And enjoy your meal. I'm sure you will like it."
    W "Y disfruta de tu comida. Seguro que te gustará."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:613
translate spanish kk_meal_cd7b009d:

    # "You start eating your long anticipated meal."
    "Empiezas a comer tu tan esperada comida."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:614
translate spanish kk_meal_991c2f81:

    # "[W] wasn't wrong when she said she expected you to enjoy it."
    "[W] no se equivocó cuando dijo que esperaba que la disfrutara."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:615
translate spanish kk_meal_bea384fc:

    # "The stew is surprisingly well seasoned, the meat melting on your tongue, and the temperature is perfect."
    "El guiso está sorprendentemente bien condimentado, la carne se derrite en la lengua y la temperatura es perfecta."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:616
translate spanish kk_meal_126f712c:

    # "The wait was truly worth it and Kateryna perfected [W]'s already good recipe."
    "La espera ha merecido realmente la pena y Kateryna ha perfeccionado la ya buena receta de [W]."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:617
translate spanish kk_meal_f5f6caaa:

    # Zt "Now, that's tasty!"
    Zt "¡Esto sí que está sabroso!"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:621
translate spanish kk_meal_014bf448:

    # "Meanwhile, in another room..."
    "Mientras tanto, en otra habitación..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:628
translate spanish kk36_5531089b:

    # W "So tell me, Kateryna..."
    W "Dime, Kateryna..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:631
translate spanish kk36_3e782da9:

    # W "I know that you like my husband, but I wonder what draws a young woman like you to him."
    W "Sé que te gusta mi marido, pero me pregunto qué atrae a una joven como tú hacia él."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:632
translate spanish kk36_9fc967f4:

    # W "Not that I mind, but I am curious..."
    W "No es que me moleste, pero tengo curiosidad..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:633
translate spanish kk36_940c7498:

    # W "You couldn't keep your eyes off him since you met him..."
    W "No has podido apartar los ojos de él desde que lo conociste..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:636
translate spanish kk36_0fe1b474:

    # W "Is it his age, his experience, his role in this House? Tell me..."
    W "¿Es su edad, su experiencia, su papel en esta Casa? Dime..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:639
translate spanish kk36_d264d5ac:

    # Ka "I'm... not sure, I think."
    Ka "Yo... no estoy segura, creo que..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:640
translate spanish kk36_5f430864:

    # Ka "Little bit of everything?"
    Ka "¿Un poco de todo?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:643
translate spanish kk36_bc35076f:

    # W "I know that you left your home with your uncle."
    W "Sé que abandonaste tu casa junto con tu tío."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:644
translate spanish kk36_35bf6531:

    # W "You have travelled a long way... was it only to see the world?"
    W "Has viajado mucho... ¿fue sólo para ver el mundo?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:645
translate spanish kk36_e91d39ea:

    # W "Or is there more to it?"
    W "¿O hay algo más?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:648
translate spanish kk36_74996b4c:

    # Ka "I... I was curious how other people live..."
    Ka "Yo... Tenía curiosidad por saber cómo viven otras personas..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:649
translate spanish kk36_1de17ea1:

    # Ka "To... see if there are safe places..."
    Ka "Para... ver si hay lugares seguros..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:652
translate spanish kk36_1fa700da:

    # W "Safe places? Your old home was not safe?"
    W "¿Lugares seguros? ¿Tu antigua casa no era segura?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:655
translate spanish kk36_4b71c739:

    # Ka "Not always... we lived in village... bandits often come to steal or hurt us..."
    Ka "No siempre... vivíamos en un pueblo... los bandidos venían a menudo a robar o a hacernos daño..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:656
translate spanish kk36_d6853f11:

    # Ka "They come every year. Sometimes more... the men always try to defend the village. Many of them die..."
    Ka "Vienen todos los años. Incluso a veces... los hombres siempre intentan defender la aldea. Muchos de ellos mueren..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:657
translate spanish kk36_c6f15c0e:

    # Ka "The village try to prepare for next attack, but it gets harder every year."
    Ka "La aldea intenta prepararse para el próximo ataque, pero cada año es más difícil."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:660
translate spanish kk36_07810d85:

    # W "And how do they prepare? Do they try to repopulate...?"
    W "¿Y cómo los preparan? ¿Intentan repoblar...?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:663
translate spanish kk36_1f62089b:

    # Ka "Yes... they try to make more babies, so they help when they grow up."
    Ka "Sí... intentan hacer más bebés, para que ayuden cuando crezcan."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:666
translate spanish kk36_ee089172:

    # Ka "But it becomes difficult... many young boys fight to defend now, too..."
    Ka "Pero se hace difícil... muchos jóvenes luchan para defenderse también ahora..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:669
translate spanish kk36_d78dd82e:

    # W "And what do your people do for that...?"
    W "¿Y qué hace tu pueblo para eso...?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:676
translate spanish kk36_84682755:

    # Ka "We have tradition in our village..."
    Ka "Tenemos una tradición en nuestro pueblo..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:677
translate spanish kk36_b3cb51c6:

    # Ka "When a woman is ready to make babies, men gather around to make her receive..."
    Ka "Cuando una mujer está preparada para tener hijos, los hombres se reúnen para hacerla recibir..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:681
translate spanish kk36_36d5bbae:

    # Ka "They take her all night, all man take turn... they make sure to breed her..."
    Ka "La cogen toda la noche, todos los hombres se turnan... se aseguran de reproducirla..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:682
translate spanish kk36_28c4d450:

    # Ka "...when night is over, the woman always is pregnant..."
    Ka "... cuando la noche termina, la mujer siempre está embarazada..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:689
translate spanish kk36_a4a2622e:

    # W "What about you... you are a pretty girl..."
    W "Y tú... eres una chica guapa..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:693
translate spanish kk36_4f5f57fc:

    # W "Did they take you, too...?"
    W "¿También te han cogido a ti...?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:697
translate spanish kk36_83b7a7eb:

    # Ka "..."
    Ka "..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:698
translate spanish kk36_6be5d2c6:

    # W "I'm sure they talked about you..."
    W "Seguro que hablaron de ti..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:699
translate spanish kk36_e0004ff0:

    # W "A young and healthy girl like you, at the perfect age to bear children..."
    W "Una chica joven y sana como tú, en la edad perfecta para tener hijos..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:706
translate spanish kk36_ace7a43f:

    # Ka "They told my mother... that they wanted, soon..."
    Ka "Le dijeron a mi madre... que querían, pronto..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:707
translate spanish kk36_bacf5615:

    # Ka "...mother told me, I go with uncle instead."
    Ka "... mi madre me dijo que me fuera con mi tío."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:708
translate spanish kk36_39af78fd:

    # Ka "When he visited, she said I must go... see safer places..."
    Ka "Cuando él la visitó, ella la dijo que debía irme... a ver lugares más seguros..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:709
translate spanish kk36_018c347e:

    # Ka "...I listened and left..."
    Ka "... la hice caso y me fui..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:713
translate spanish kk36_86733d95:

    # W "I see, then..."
    W "Ya veo, pues..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:714
translate spanish kk36_1693e1f5:

    # W "That was interesting."
    W "Eso fue interesante."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:715
translate spanish kk36_c0ec37ea:

    # W "But [persistent.player_name!c] is probably waiting for us. Want to head back?"
    W "Pero [persistent.player_name!c] probablemente nos esté esperando. ¿Quieres volver?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:724
translate spanish kk36_b10f1dba:

    # W "[persistent.player_name] told me you showed interest in the temple and the priestesses?"
    W "[persistent.player_name] me dijo que mostrabas interés por el templo y las sacerdotisas."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:725
translate spanish kk36_d3951b39:

    # W "Is that why? Do they remind you of home?"
    W "¿Es por eso? ¿Te recuerdan a tu hogar?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:726
translate spanish kk36_865d6a95:

    # Kaw "Mhm... But also very different."
    Kaw "Mhm... Pero también es muy diferentes."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:727
translate spanish kk36_b706c3c9:

    # Ww "That is why you are curious about making babies, isn't it..."
    Ww "Por eso sientes curiosidad por hacer bebés, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:728
translate spanish kk36_8d824f13:

    # Ww "You wonder if you are made for this, no...?"
    Ww "Te preguntas si estás hecha para esto, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:729
translate spanish kk36_83b7a7eb_1:

    # Ka "..."
    Ka "..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:732
translate spanish kk36_15ef3868:

    # Ww "Let me take a better look at you, then. Maybe I can give you some advice..."
    Ww "Deja que te mire mejor, entonces. Quizá pueda darte algún consejo..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:734
translate spanish kk36_343dea9f:

    # Ww "I do know a few things about making babies..."
    Ww "Sé algunas cosas sobre cómo hacer bebés..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:740
translate spanish kk36_83b7a7eb_2:

    # Ka "..."
    Ka "..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:741
translate spanish kk36_98ebe351:

    # Ww "Look at you..."
    Ww "Mírate..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:744
translate spanish kk36_49dec6d1:

    # Ww "I'm sure they were furious when you left..."
    Ww "Seguro que se pusieron furiosos cuando te fuiste..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:747
translate spanish kk36_6251d348:

    # Kaw "Do you... think?"
    Kaw "¿Tú... lo crees?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:748
translate spanish kk36_7b2c52c7:

    # Ww "I'm sure of that."
    Ww "Estoy segura de ello."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:749
translate spanish kk36_396a0988:

    # Kaw "[persistent.player_name] said same... to me..."
    Kaw "[persistent.player_name] me dijo lo mismo..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:750
translate spanish kk36_2f410026:

    # Kaw "You think he likes me...?"
    Kaw "¿Crees que le gusto?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:753
translate spanish kk36_08fc94a9:

    # Ww "I think he does... he thinks you're cute."
    Ww "Creo que sí... el cree que eres linda."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:756
translate spanish kk36_bd7974af:

    # Ww "I'm sure he would like to see what I am seeing now..."
    Ww "Seguro que a él le gustaría ver lo que yo estoy viendo ahora..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:759
translate spanish kk36_19437ddf:

    # Ww "But tell me again... what do you like about him?"
    Ww "Pero dime de nuevo... ¿qué te gusta de él?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:762
translate spanish kk36_c037c2b2:

    # Ww "And why not be open and direct about it?"
    Ww "¿Y por qué no eres abierta y directa al respecto?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:763
translate spanish kk36_55972486:

    # Ww "Why is that...?"
    Ww "¿Por qué es eso...?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:766
translate spanish kk36_58eae9f5:

    # Ka "I... am not sure if... I can stay here..."
    Ka "Yo... no estoy segura de si... puedo quedarme aquí..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:767
translate spanish kk36_760879f3:

    # Ka "...is safe here... but he is your man... you have family..."
    Ka "... aquí es seguro... pero él es tu hombre... tú tienes familia..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:768
translate spanish kk36_c1ec9188:

    # Ka "This is not my place... I think."
    Ka "Este no es mi lugar... creo."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:771
translate spanish kk36_2acddc43:

    # W "Hm..."
    W "Hm..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:774
translate spanish kk36_b8562abb:

    # W "Follow me, will you..."
    W "Sígueme, ¿quieres?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:775
translate spanish kk36_1d01f8ac:

    # "She leads Kateryna to the bed, and gently pushes her back, on top of it..."
    "Lleva a Kateryna a la cama y la empuja suavemente hacia atrás, encima de ella..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:778
translate spanish kk36_0b6dcb49:

    # Ka "Hnh...?"
    Ka "¿Unh...?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:781
translate spanish kk36_6d1e608c:

    # W "So you're not sure if you would fit in here, are you..."
    W "Así que no estás segura de si encajarías aquí, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:784
translate spanish kk36_cc0b6b15:

    # Ka "I... don't know..."
    Ka "Yo... no lo sé..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:787
translate spanish kk36_807b40c3:

    # "As Kateryna doesn't seem to know how to react, [W] takes a good look at the girl in front of her."
    "Como Kateryna no parece saber cómo reaccionar, [W] mira bien a la chica que tiene delante."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:790
translate spanish kk36_4e54414f:

    # W "What to do with a girl like you..."
    W "Qué hacer con una chica como tú..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:793
translate spanish kk36_cfcdb749:

    # W "You are right when you say that he is my man, Kateryna."
    W "Tienes razón cuando dices que es mi hombre, Kateryna."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:794
translate spanish kk36_0e73dca1:

    # W "Not every girl who comes here is aware of what that means, of how deep that goes..."
    W "No todas las chicas que vienen aquí son conscientes de lo que eso significa, de lo profundo que es..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:797
translate spanish kk36_a1a5d3fe:

    # W "But I know my husband better than you do."
    W "Pero yo conozco a mi marido mejor que tú."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:798
translate spanish kk36_51a4cab3:

    # Ww "And if he saw you like this..."
    Ww "Y si te viera así..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:801
translate spanish kk36_a11b49ae:

    # Ww "I promise you he would have a hard time stopping himself from doing... many delicious things to you."
    Ww "te prometo que le costaría mucho dejar de hacerte... muchas cosas deliciosas."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:802
translate spanish kk36_ea2dbd2f:

    # Ww "Tell me, before you fled the men of your village, did you have any experiences...?"
    Ww "Dime, antes de huir de los hombres de tu pueblo, ¿has tenido alguna experiencia...?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:805
translate spanish kk36_9c3670d2:

    # Kaw "No... I never have..."
    Kaw "No... Nunca la he tenido..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:806
translate spanish kk36_27d5b568:

    # Kaw "My mother would try protect me..."
    Kaw "Mi madre intentaba protegerme..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:807
translate spanish kk36_f9b77860:

    # Ww "And what about a kiss? Did anyone truly kiss you, yet...?"
    Ww "¿Y qué hay de un beso? ¿Alguien te ha besado de verdad, ya...?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:810
translate spanish kk36_874ed1cc:

    # Kaw "I..."
    Kaw "Yo..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:811
translate spanish kk36_9a288683:

    # Kaw "...did not..."
    Kaw "... no lo hice..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:814
translate spanish kk36_a11b923e:

    # Ww "It's good that I asked, then. Because I was about to do exactly that..."
    Ww "Es bueno que lo haya preguntado, pues. Porque estaba a punto de hacer exactamente eso..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:815
translate spanish kk36_7d3f080a:

    # Ww "I know that things must be very confusing for you now."
    Ww "Sé que las cosas deben ser muy confusas para ti ahora."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:816
translate spanish kk36_3d2f3cd4:

    # Ww "You left your home, and now you wonder what you want to do, and where you belong..."
    Ww "Dejaste tu hogar, y ahora te preguntas qué quieres hacer, y a dónde perteneces..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:817
translate spanish kk36_2072449e:

    # Ww "Take your time and think of what you really want."
    Ww "Tómate tu tiempo y piensa en lo que realmente quieres."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:818
translate spanish kk36_a6c64862:

    # Ww "You will always be welcome, whether you come for [persistent.player_name], to have a bit of time for yourself away from Igor, or to exchange recipes..."
    Ww "Siempre serás bienvenida, tanto si vienes por [persistent.player_name], para tener un poco de tiempo para ti misma lejos de Igor, o para intercambiar recetas..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:819
translate spanish kk36_11da5ecb:

    # Ww "...and if you ever decide to stay, this house is large enough..."
    Ww "... y si alguna vez decides quedarte, esta casa es lo suficientemente grande..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:820
translate spanish kk36_02cd8249:

    # Ww "...and I'm sure that we will find something for you to do."
    Ww "... y estoy segura de que encontraremos algo que hacer para ti."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:821
translate spanish kk36_68d9f519:

    # Ww "I promise that you would not feel alone here, ever..."
    Ww "Te prometo que aquí no te sentirás sola, nunca..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:824
translate spanish kk36_83b7a7eb_3:

    # Ka "..."
    Ka "..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:835
translate spanish kk_end_c420885b:

    # Zt "That was delicious... I am full."
    Zt "Ha sido delicioso... Estoy lleno."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:839
translate spanish kk_end_3a0b100c:

    # "You hear the door opening."
    "Oyes cómo se abre la puerta."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:840
translate spanish kk_end_7db47a2d:

    # "Kateryna rushes in, visibly excited..."
    "Kateryna entra corriendo, visiblemente emocionada..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:843
translate spanish kk_end_81a189ef:

    # Ka "[persistent.player_name], I am sorry, I am late. How did you like your meal?"
    Ka "[persistent.player_name], lo siento, llego tarde. ¿Qué te ha parecido la comida?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:846
translate spanish kk_end_b19ac0c2:

    # Z "It was great."
    Z "Ha estado muy bien."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:847
translate spanish kk_end_4428739c:

    # Z "[W] can cook really well, but whatever you did with her dish gave it a new twist that I really liked."
    Z "[W] sabe cocinar muy bien, pero lo que hiciste con su plato le dio un nuevo giro que me gustó mucho."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:848
translate spanish kk_end_699cf589:

    # Z "You really know what you're doing, in the kitchen."
    Z "Realmente sabes lo que haces, en la cocina."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:851
translate spanish kk_end_0608b8cd:

    # Ka "Oh..."
    Ka "Oh..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:852
translate spanish kk_end_fea67d72:

    # "She blushes..."
    "Ella se sonroja..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:855
translate spanish kk_end_d4fe7bdd:

    # "She comes closer..."
    "Se acerca..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:858
translate spanish kk_end_601411bb:

    # "She kisses you on your cheek..."
    "Te besa en la mejilla..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:861
translate spanish kk_end_45ba169d:

    # Ka "Thank you for compliment, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ka "Gracias por el cumplido, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:862
translate spanish kk_end_0f2e51fb:

    # Ka "I spoke to [W], it was really nice. I like her a lot!"
    Ka "He hablado con [W], ha sido muy agradable. ¡Me gusta mucho!"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:863
translate spanish kk_end_b0d1d591:

    # Ka "I hope I can come here again, maybe?"
    Ka "Espero poder venir aquí de nuevo, ¿tal vez?"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:866
translate spanish kk_end_9dc117bb:

    # Z "Of course, you're always welcome here."
    Z "Por supuesto, aquí siempre serás bienvenida."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:869
translate spanish kk_end_33dc91db:

    # Ka "Thank you! And I will help out with cooking again, too! Make dish you have never tasted."
    Ka "Gracias. ¡Y también ayudaré a cocinar de nuevo! Haré un plato que nunca hayas probado."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:873
translate spanish kk_end_15213bce:

    # Ka "{i}*kiss*"
    Ka "{i}*beso*"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:876
translate spanish kk_end_a8c61b1d:

    # "She kisses you on the cheek again, lingering for a second..."
    "Te besa de nuevo en la mejilla, deteniéndose un segundo..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:879
translate spanish kk_end_bcd217f5:

    # "Her kiss feels lovely, and after your last close encounter, holding back does not come easy."
    "Su beso es encantador, y después de vuestro último encuentro cercano, contenerse no resulta fácil."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:880
translate spanish kk_end_8695a0a3:

    # "But in the end her joyful excitement wins you over, and you decide to not spoil that for her by taking things further."
    "Pero al final su alegre excitación te gana, y decides no estropear eso para ella llevando las cosas más lejos."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:883
translate spanish kk_end_43ae6bbb:

    # Ka "I will go home now. See you soon, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ka "Me voy a casa. Hasta pronto, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:886
translate spanish kk_end_96a3ee4c:

    # Z "See you soon, Kateryna. Send your Uncle my regards."
    Z "Hasta pronto, Kateryna. Envía a tu tío mis saludos."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:889
translate spanish kk_end_c377f34f:

    # Ka "I will. Bye!"
    Ka "Lo haré. ¡Adiós!"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:896
translate spanish kk_end_29a2de66:

    # "She leaves..."
    "Ella se va..."

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:900
translate spanish kk_end_87efdd2b:

    # Ka "Bye!!"
    Ka "¡¡Adiós!!"

# game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:906
translate spanish kk_end_29a2de66_1:

    # "She leaves..."
    "Ella se va..."

