    # game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:519
    old "\"You could say that.\""
    new "\"Se podría decir que sí.\""

    # game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:519
    old "\"Not really.\""
    new "\"En realidad no.\""

    # game/scripts/kitchen.rpy:895
    old "Kateryna decided to visit me spontaneously. It turns out she really knows her way around a kitchen. It was nice to learn of something she is passionate about."
    new "Kateryna decidió visitarme espontáneamente. Resulta que realmente sabe desenvolverse en la cocina. Fue agradable descubrir algo que le apasiona."
